    <h1>Crawl Trap</h1>
    <p class="description">A structural issue that traps search-engine crawlers in <strong>infinite URL loops</strong>. Faceted nav, calendars, and session IDs are the classic culprits - each capable of hiding <strong>millions of URLs</strong> from a site's real page count.</p>
